column5: Check out how many perch were inside this 29' pike.  Impressive!  Definition of Gluttony! https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10150391461864528&set=a.440874564527.259221.237937184527&type=1&ref=nf
LOL!!!  Some of the giant whities I bring home from Simcoe look very similar filled with smelt/emerald shiners.
When they are on the feed it is amazing how much they will swallow.
17 smelts in a Brook Trout is my most impressive story. Unless I include the T Bone that my co worker ate last winter in Dryden.
that looks like the "fool pike" syndrome, she doesn't know when she's full
